div.p:
A. Whoever imports, exports, or transmits merchandise, liable to duty, or
                            takes the same out of the public warehouse, against the rules and
                            regulations;

D. Whoever appears with merchandise, liable to duty, and passes the
                            custom-house for one hundred yards without being at liberty to do
                            so;

H. Whoever appears across the line in Switzerland with merchandise liable
                            to paying duty at the closed hours, against the rules and
                            regulations;
